ASTRONOMICAL DATA LICENSES

This software accesses public astronomical survey data. The data itself has
separate usage terms:

- NASA/SkyView data: Public Domain (U.S. Government Work)
- 2MASS data: Public Domain
- DSS data: Free for research/education with attribution
- WISE data: Public Domain (NASA)

See README.md and claude.md for complete data usage rights and attribution
requirements.
